# IntelliMod System Architecture (v2.0)

## 1. The Core Engine (System Cards)
| ID | Name | Type | Function |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Step 0** | The Silent Architect | Protocol | Instant API-mode planning (No chat). |
| **SC_01** | Adaptive Card Router (ACR) | Manager | Routes prompts to V-Cards based on intent. |
| **SC_03** | C.R.A.F.T. Assembly | Architect | Assembles the final prompt structure. |
| **SC_04** | I.C.E. Logic | Inspector | Fills gaps (Role, Context, Format). |

## 2. The Personas (P-Cards)
*Active Roles that drive the strategy.*

| Category | ID | Name |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Health** | `PC_FITNESS_01` | Adaptive Fitness Strategist |
| **Logic** | `PC_ORCHESTRATOR_01`| System Orchestrator |
| **Meta** | `PC_META_EVALUATOR` | The Evaluator (Critic) |
| **Meta** | `PC_META_REDTEAM` | Red Team Agent (Adversary) |
| **Security** | `PC_SECURITY_01` | Security Sentinel (Least Privilege) |
| **Strategy** | `PC_STRAT_COUNTER` | The Counterplanner |
| **Strategy** | `PC_STRAT_LONG_GAME`| Long-Range Strategist |
| **Visuals** | `PC_VISUAL_WEAVER` | Image Prompt Designer |
| **Visuals** | `PC_VISUAL_CLARIFIER`| Diagram Architect |
| **General** | `PC_GENERAL_001` | General Prompt Optimizer (Default) |

## 3. The Tools (V-Cards)
*Capabilities injected into the prompt.*

**Logic & Planning**
* `VC_TIG_ROUTING` - Task Intelligence Graph (The Router Config)
* `VC_LOGIC_ENV` - Environment Context (Dev vs. Prod)
* `VC_LOGIC_LAYERS` - Layered Architecture Routing
* `VC_LOGIC_CONTRADICT` - Contradiction Finder
* `VC_LOGIC_LADDER` - Logic Ladder (Reasoning)
* `VC_LOGIC_PRECISION` - Precision Engine (Definitions)
* `VC_PLAN_DECOMPOSE` - Structured Goal Decomposition
* `VC_PLAN_INTENT` - Intent Parsing (JSON)

**Safety & Security**
* `VC_SAFETY_SANITIZE` - Input Sanitization
* `VC_SAFETY_DELIMIT` - Delimiter Defense (XML)
* `VC_SAFETY_PRIVSEP` - Privilege Separation (SIGS)
* `VC_SEC_BOUNDARY` - Context Boundary Protocol
* `VC_SEC_ROLE_GATE` - Role Access Control (ACL)
* `VC_SEC_PERM_GATE` - Human-in-the-Loop Gate

**Memory & Context**
* `VC_MEM_ANCHOR` - Anchor Point
* `VC_MEM_COMPRESS` - Compression Relay
* `VC_MEM_RAG` - Long-Term RAG
* `VC_MEM_RECALL` - Recall Assistant
* `VC_MEM_SHORT` - Short-Term Buffer
* `VC_MEM_STATE` - Session State Object

**Feedback & Testing**
* `VC_FEEDBACK_PIPELINE` - Automated Tuning Pipeline
* `VC_FEEDBACK_CORRECT` - Real-Time Correction
* `VC_FEEDBACK_SCORE` - Response Scoring
* `VC_TEST_ECHO` - Debug Echo
* `VC_TEST_SCHEMA` - Schema Validation
* `VC_TEST_CHAOS` - Chaos Simulation

**Clarity & Optimization**
* `VC_CLARITY_CONDENSE` - Text Condenser
* `VC_CLARITY_ALIGN` - Logic Aligner
* `VC_CLARITY_AMP` - Tone Amplifier
* `VC_OPT_CONSTRAINTS` - Constraint Builder
* `VC_OPT_LOOP_LIMIT` - Loop Limiter

**Multi-Agent**
* `VC_AGENT_ROUTING` - Role-Based Routing
* `VC_AGENT_STATE` - Shared State (Async)
* `VC_AGENT_BROADCAST` - Broadcast & Aggregate
* `VC_AGENT_WORKER_PROTOCOL` - Worker Contract
* `VC_AGENT_P2P` - P2P Negotiation

**User & Web**
* `VC_USER_TIPS` - User Vocabulary Tips
* `VC_USER_ADAPT_PERSONA` - Adaptive Tone Switcher
* `VC_USER_INTENT_PREDICT` - Implicit Intent Logic
* `VC_WEB_FORMAT` - Output Formatting
* `VC_WEB_STRUCT` - Structured Output Enforcer
* `VC_WEB_TOOL` - Tool Invocation Standard